<h2 id="about-the-site">About the site</h2>
<p>This is a personal website of LiXizhi, created with github and jekyll. 
Create your own website is as easy as clone or fork a <a href="https://github.com/LiXizhi/lixizhi.github.io">template</a> on github, and <a href="http://jekyllrb.com/docs/posts/">commit</a> to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">_posts</code> folder.</p>

